#  26 Feb 2013 - R. Yantosca - Added MAX_DEP for Input_Opt
#  19 Mar 2013 - R. Yantosca - Added LINOZ fields for Input_Opt
#  19 Mar 2013 - R. Yantosca - MAX_TRCS should be 53, not 54
